===more:In this chapter (30), we see the significance of new ideals and ideologies and how they inspire people to alter or to form new governments. Which ideology or ideal do you think was most important or had longer lasting repercussions? Why did they have such powerful effects? In what ways are these ideals or ideologies evident today?
